OL,5, Dozens of taxi drivers have protested  
OL,6, outside Glasgow city chambers over the 
OL,7, "horrendous" state of the city's roads.
OL,9,FThe motorists, who say their cars have 
OL,10,Fbeen badly damaged by reported         
OL,11,Fpotholes, sounded their horns on a slow
OL,12,Fdrive-by on Saturday afternoon.        
OL,14,FMeanwhile campaigners gathered on      
OL,15,FGeorge Square calling for the council  
OL,16,Fto declare a "pothole emergency".      
OL,18,FThe council said it expects to have    
OL,19,Fcompleted around 175 road re-surfacing 
OL,20,Fprojects by March this year.           
